Package net.rtccloud.sdk.event.call

Package that holds all CallEvent event subclasses

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AudioRouteEvent
    Event that is fired when the Call.AudioRoute of a Call has changed
    CallEvent
    Base class for all Call events.
    CreatedEvent
    Event that is fired when a Call is created.
    FloorListEvent
    Event fired when the floor list has changed
    InbandDataChannelEvent
    Event fired when receiving data through the inband DataChannel
    ParticipantEvent
    Event fired when a Contact has changed
    ParticipantListEvent
    Event fired when the participant list has changed
    PointerEvent
    Event fired when receiving a pointer event
    RecordingEvent
    Event fired when the call start or stop recording
    ScreenShareInEvent
    Event fired when you are now receiving screen share or not anymore
    ScreenShareInSizeEvent
    Event fired when you are now receiving screen share with another dimension
    ScreenShareOutEvent
    Event fired when you are now sending screen share or not anymore
    SipEvent
    Event fired when the Call obtains its SIP id
    StatusEvent
    Event that is fired when the Call.CallStatus of a Call has changed.
    VideoInEvent
    Event fired when you are now receiving video or not anymore
    VideoInSizeEvent
    Event fired when you are now receiving video with another dimension and maybe another Call.VideoProfile
    VideoOutEvent
    Event fired when you are now sending video or not anymore
    VideoOutSizeEvent
    Event fired when you are now sending video with another dimension
